---
title: Family-Style Pizza Party 2x the delicious portions!
description: Time for a pizza party right in your own kitchen—no delivery required! You'll stretch and shape our pre-made dough, then top with marinara, mozzarella, bell pepper, caramelized onion, and pepperoni. Brush those golden crusts with garlic butter, sprinkle with Parmesan, and serve with balsamic-dressed side salad and ranch for dipping.
